    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear in the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely require some routine maintenance, such as new tires and a brake service, in the near future. It\u2019s a solid option for someone looking for functional transportation at a lower price point who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and mechanical projects.",
