    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative example, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. This is a rare opportunity to secure an investment-grade automobile of the highest caliber.",
      "price": 48900.0,
